        <title>cpp输入输出提速底层分析</title>
        <link>https://baozi.github.io/p/cpp%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E6%8F%90%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%95%E5%B1%82%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/</link>
